& ~/ is equal to perform
& ~| is equal to stop
& ~: is equal to given
& ~- is equal to redo
& ~^ is equal to till
& ~+ is equal to span
& ~% is equal to iter
& ~* is equal to further
& ~$ is equal to fulfil

~/name(params)
	& <perform body>
~|

~: yes == yes ~*
	& <given body>
~|

~-
	& <redo body>
~^ yes == yes

~+ yes ~$
	& <span body>
	end
~|

~% i = 1, 10 ~$
	& <iter body>
~|